OL,5,CCALL FOR CLARITY                       
OL,6,G                                       
OL,7, The European Commission looks set to   
OL,8,Gcall for all consumer foods to carry   
OL,9,Glabels saying whether they contain     
OL,10,Ggenetically modified ingredients.      
OL,12,GUnder the plans all seeds, animal feeds
OL,13,Gand consumer foods must state clearly  
OL,14,Gwhether they do, do not, or may,       
OL,15,Gcontain modified materials.            
OL,17,GThe 20 commissioners will propose      
OL,18,Glegislation in the autumn to replace   
OL,19,Gexisting measures.                     
